WITH activated_tokens_without_vote AS (
                SELECT token
                FROM token
                WHERE
                    state = 'activated'::token_state
                    AND token NOT IN (
                        SELECT token_token AS token
                        FROM has_voted
                        WHERE voting_id = $1
                    )
            )
            SELECT count(*) as "count!"
            FROM activated_tokens_without_vote
